A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Judge Holly W. Veal on her outstanding public service; and
2 for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Judge Holly W. Veal has long been recognized by the citizens of this state for
4 the vital role that she has played in leadership and her deep personal commitment to the
5 welfare of the citizens of Georgia; and
6 WHEREAS, she has diligently and conscientiously devoted innumerable hours of her time,
7 talents, and energy toward the betterment of her community and state, as evidenced
8 dramatically by her superlative service with the Superior Court of Henry County; and
9 WHEREAS, Judge Veal is a trailblazer in the legal profession, serving as the first
10 Guyanese/African American as well as the first woman to hold a judgeship in the Superior
11 Court of Henry County; and
12 WHEREAS, throughout her distinguished career, she has been recognized by her peers and
13 colleagues for her exemplary advocacy, having argued cases before the Supreme Court of
14 Georgia, and her dedication to ethical standards in the legal profession is reflected in her
15 service on the Formal Advisory Opinion Board through the State Bar of Georgia; and
